        "description": {
            "value": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; display: block;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Holy</em> weapons command powerful celestial energy. A weapon with this rune deals an extra [[/r 1d6 # good]] good damage against evil targets. If you are evil, you are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 2} while carrying or wielding this weapon.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; display: block;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Activate </strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; font-family: Pathfinder2eActions; font-size: 1.8em;\">R </span>command;&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Frequency</strong>&nbsp;once per day;&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Trigger</strong>&nbsp;You critically succeed at an attack roll against an evil creature with the weapon;&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Effect</strong>&nbsp;You regain HP equal to double the evil creature's level. This is a good, positive, healing effect.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; display: block;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Craft Requirements</strong>&nbsp;You are good.</span></p>"
